        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "When trying to use Zend_Soap_Wsdl with an uri containing \"&\" char, I have the following bug:\r\n\r\n{quote}Warning: DOMDocument::loadXML() [domdocument.loadxml]: EntityRef: expecting ';' in Entity, line: 2 in \/Zend\/Soap\/Wsdl.php on line 108\r\nWarning: DOMDocument::loadXML() [domdocument.loadxml]: EntityRef: expecting ';' in Entity, line: 4 in \/Zend\/Soap\/Wsdl.php on line 108\r\nException: Unable to create DomDocument{quote}\r\n\r\nThe problem comes from line 91 to 98 in Zend\/Soap\/Wsdl.php :\r\n\r\n        {code}$wsdl = \"<?xml version='1.0' ?>\r\n                <definitions name='$name' targetNamespace='$uri'\r\n                    xmlns='http:\/\/schemas.xmlsoap.org\/wsdl\/'\r\n                    xmlns:tns='$uri'\r\n                    xmlns:soap='http:\/\/schemas.xmlsoap.org\/wsdl\/soap\/'\r\n                    xmlns:xsd='http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2001\/XMLSchema'\r\n                    xmlns:soap-enc='http:\/\/schemas.xmlsoap.org\/soap\/encoding\/'\r\n                    xmlns:wsdl='http:\/\/schemas.xmlsoap.org\/wsdl\/'><\/definitions>\";{code}\r\n\r\nThe following replacement works perfectly:\r\n\r\n{code}$wsdl = \"<?xml version='1.0' ?>\r\n                <definitions name='$name' targetNamespace='\".htmlentities($uri).\"'\r\n                    xmlns='http:\/\/schemas.xmlsoap.org\/wsdl\/'\r\n                    xmlns:tns='\".htmlentities($uri).\"'\r\n                    xmlns:soap='http:\/\/schemas.xmlsoap.org\/wsdl\/soap\/'\r\n                    xmlns:xsd='http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2001\/XMLSchema'\r\n                    xmlns:soap-enc='http:\/\/schemas.xmlsoap.org\/soap\/encoding\/'\r\n                    xmlns:wsdl='http:\/\/schemas.xmlsoap.org\/wsdl\/'><\/definitions>\";{code}\r\n"
        },
